snippet.title: Holstin - Announce Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Holstin is coming PS4 and PS5.

Holstin is set in an eerie, isolated 90s Polish lakeside town in which an ominous presence has slowly enveloped everything and everyone. Scavenge for supplies, fight twisted monstrosities and deal with residents slowly losing their sanity to uncover the truth of what went wrong in this once pristine town.

#ps5games #ps5 #ps4 #ps4games
